WEBVTT

00:04:26.901 --> 00:04:33.800
Will they ever know or care
that I'm chained?

00:04:35.246 --> 00:04:42.363
Is there redemption for the sin
of my younger days?

00:04:42.363 --> 00:04:46.308
Because I've changed.

00:04:46.308 --> 00:04:50.390
Lord knows I've changed.

00:04:50.390 --> 00:04:55.596
I am a prisoner
for the wrong I've done.

00:04:55.596 --> 00:04:58.916
I'm doing time here.
This is not my home.

00:04:58.916 --> 00:05:03.630
Dream of freedom, hope for mercy.